{"tid":486901,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"珍惜初戀!!!","createTime":"2017-12-02T09:01:40.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T09:25:35.000Z","uid":125127,"like":32,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ef07e52dcc1937805e3e87994a81721a5e40d3b0","tid":486901,"uid":125127,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:01:40.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住</span></span><br />\n所有野都係第一次最深刻<br />\n你會帶住最純真嘅心去付出<br />\n你會不顧一切咁去愛<br />\n你會第一次為左一個人改變自己<br />\n好簡單 冇原因<br />\n只係因為你愛佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住</span></span><br />\n就算大家過左熱戀期<br />\n開始磨合嘅時候<br />\n發現開始感受唔到當初嘅愛<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">唔好放棄!!!</span></span><br />\n可能去到某個地步你好想分手<br />\n但係呢個時候先係兩個人啱啱開始<br />\n一有呢個念頭就要問自己<br />\n當初點解會鍾意佢<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">記住</span></span><br />\n初戀係一世都唔會忘記<br />\n所以一定要盡全力去愛<br />\n唔可以浪費左呢個一生人一次嘅機會<br />\n否則你冇資格話盡全力去愛只會受傷<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">祝天下尚有初戀者要好好去愛<br />\n情侶彼此都係初戀嘅更加要好好珍惜</span>"},{"pid":"0e9ded42e3229387f66f7428070a14522e3c3e46","tid":486901,"uid":74262,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:10:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ae597202d30217a10bf529f6934410828086d8bc","tid":486901,"uid":125127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:22:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 女孩既初夜就係咁既感覺</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 情路上雖然盡是人渣同無奈<br />\n希望大家都可以有少少正能量捱得過"},{"pid":"5739d3e89f85311d08272daecf230472aa1bc81c","tid":486901,"uid":44201,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:26:01.000Z","msg":"而我就唔識珍惜 結果後悔得太遲"},{"pid":"348052a1ce05dfce43f731498be4b6d8c001faa0","tid":486901,"uid":125127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:37:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>而我就唔識珍惜 結果後悔得太遲</blockquote><br />\n可能呢段關係嘅終點唔係一生一世<br />\n咁就要努力去行之後嘅路"},{"pid":"6a70a8b65426b21788ce955320d5e15e19031771","tid":486901,"uid":37131,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T09:39:21.000Z","msg":"算吧啦，自己記住咁多野有咩用<br />\n一隻手係拍唔響"},{"pid":"a3ae4e61988d1406874442e093e9bd339e554fd9","tid":486901,"uid":125127,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T10:05:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>算吧啦，自己記住咁多野有咩用<br />\n一隻手係拍唔響</blockquote><br />\n失望係因為有期望<br />\n自己出盡力一次兩次三次<br />\n然後對方都係冇回應嘅<br />\n只可以怪人地唔識珍惜<br />\n到時自己自然會知道幾時想放棄"},{"pid":"0603526dc6fe44b5efd82e2ac73b9c4a1916405c","tid":486901,"uid":74139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T11:53:01.000Z","msg":"我幾時死心 好掛住佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6a03279a49d77ff2046f9d641e40aa9468c1b201","tid":486901,"uid":50776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:49:08.000Z","msg":"好想喊 岩岩分手"},{"pid":"3923e6b8280c288fb7627f4ab33dd64172065612","tid":486901,"uid":155715,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T01:12:52.000Z","msg":"過左熱戀期 開始磨合果陣就會分手<br />\n而我就係因為咁樣結束左我嘅初戀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"181d57c38106b80b964b726e918dbd8ef1adc5d7","tid":486901,"uid":125127,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T09:25:35.000Z","msg":"樓主我都差唔多了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔知大家仲頂到幾耐呢?"}]}